  ^^^

  12 Apr 2011; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> libconfig-1.4.7.ebuild:
  No need for eutils.eclass.

  12 Apr 2011; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> libconfig-1.4.7.ebuild:
  Define src_test to get tests run, disable building examples, optionally
  install examples, use canonical method to prevent .la files from being
  installed, thanks to Johan Bergström. Bend over backwards to install only
  the desired example files.

  12 Apr 2011; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Add maintainers.

